![screen shot 2015-06-11 at 3 19 27 pm](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/3909933/8104325/8506f2b0-104d-11e5-99b8-46f05bd5db52.png)

Look at the `var` text above. I have the following packages installed over the core packages.
- [`atom-jade`](https://atom.io/packages/atom-jade)
- [`file-icons`](https://atom.io/packages/file-icons)
- [`react`](https://atom.io/packages/react)

